PrecisAmendment to the SPECIAL SERVICES (EXCISE) REGULATIONS for the purpose of eliminating any reference to authorization of hours of service by the Deputy Minister, and thus remove any perception of sub-delegation of authority, etc.

precis:
Amendment to the SPECIAL SERVICES (EXCISE) REGULATIONS for the purpose of
eliminating any reference to authorization of hours of service by the
Deputy Minister, and thus remove any perception of sub-delegation of
authority, etc.
